zon Ki Kahani (film)|Do Lafzon Ki Kahani]]''\n| \"Ankhiyaan\"\n| [[Arjuna Harjai]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deccanchronicle.com/entertainment/bollywood/180516/watch-the-new-song-ankhiyaan-featuring-randeep-and-kajal-will-make-you-cry.html|title=Watch: Randeep and Kajal's new song Ankhiyaan will leave you teary eyed|work=Deccan Chronicle|date=18 May 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Beiimaan Love]]''\n| \"Hug Me\"\n| [[Raghav Sachar]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.in/hug-me-song-sizzling-sunny-leone-back-kanika-kapoors-catchy-track-beiimaan-love-video-683125|title='Hug Me' song: Sizzling Sunny Leone is back with Kanika Kapoor's catchy track from 'Beiimaan Love'|work=[[International Business Times]]|date=17 June 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Great Grand Masti]]''\n| \"Teri Kamar Ko\"\n| [[Sanjeev\u2013Darshan]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report-watch-the-title-track-of-great-grand-masti-is-out-2227111|title=Watch: 'Teri Kamar Ko', the title track of Great Grand Masti, is out!|work=DNA India|date=23 June 2016|accessdate=24 June 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[The Legend of Michael Mishra]]''\n| \"Luv Letter\"\n|Meet Bros\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/music/news/Watch-Aditi-Rao-Hydaris-peppy-Love-letter/articleshow/53264961.cms|title=Watch: Aditi Rao Hydari's peppy 'Love letter'|work=The Times of India|author=Kaushal, Ruchi|accessdate=18 July 2016|date=18 July 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[A Flying Jatt]]''\n| \"Beat Pe Booty\n| [[Sachin-Jigar]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.saavn.com/s/album/hindi/A-Flying-Jatt-2016/slORX8XBpsA_|title=A Flying Jatt Album at Saavn|work=[[Saavn]]|date=21 July 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Jaguar (2016 film)|Jaguar]]'' <small>(Kannada)</small>\n| \"Selfie\"\n| [[S. S. Thaman]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/in/album/jaguar-original-motion-picture/id1150410756|title=Jaguar (Original Motion Picture Soundtrack) \u2013 EP by Thaman S. on iTunes|publisher=[[iT